data.description: Golf Course Home! Lovely sun-filled 4 bedroom, 3 full bath, 3 living room home with plenty of elbow room to raise a family and entertain! Located in the Boutique Community of DeCordova Bend Estates your home boasts beautiful windows that highlights the outdoors, trees and golf course.  Enjoy outdoor living in the wrap around balcony that overlooks the golf course.  Home features a metal roof, 2 fireplaces, 3 AC units, wet bar, subway time and granite in kitchen, huge closets, wood flooring and extra large master bedroom, master bath and closet.  Fantastic views from dining, living, game room  and kitchen
